# Examples showing alternate version readers (header / media-type / query)
# These demonstrate how the API Versioning is configured in Program.cs (Url segment is primary in controllers).
# Note: the controllers in this sample use URL-segment routes; header/query/media examples are included for reference.

### Header-based (X-Api-Version)
GET {{ApiVersioning.Sample_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/blogs
X-Api-Version: 2.0
Accept: application/json

###

### Media type versioning (Accept header)
GET {{ApiVersioning.Sample_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/blogs
Accept: application/json;v=2.0

###

### Query string versioning
GET {{ApiVersioning.Sample_HostAddress}}/api/v2.0/blogs?api-version=2.0&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

